    "text": [
        "Hi Jimmy,",
        "I'm writing to tell you that there will be a public picnic in Kings Park this Sunday. In the morning there will be a chess contest, degustation of jams and live music. Also, It says that at night there will be a Ukrainian movie in the open sky, I hope you didn't forget our movie nights.",
